     else.

> EXAMINE ALL BUT THE CANDLE
Bell: it was a small golden ornament. Bottle: as I reached
for thebottle of holy water, I felt my strength drain away.
I could not move, even to step back from the bottle !

> RAM LOAD
Ok. I was inside St. Amiga's chapel, listening to the drone
