a candle.

> TAKE BELL
I took the bell. I dropped the key. (Ghosts are relatively
weak and cannot levitate many things at once).

> GO TO MEMORIAL (letting the computer work out the route
Pressany key to abandon this type of "high level" command)

I floated north and was outside St. Amiga's chapel of rest.

